        <updateDate>2021-06-09T18:04:00Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Climate Risk Disclosure Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Securities and Exchange Commission to&nbsp;require an issuer of securities to annually disclose information regarding climate change-related risks posed to the issuer, including an issuer's strategies and actions to mitigate these risks.</p> <p>Specifically, issuers must report their direct and indirect greenhouse-gas emissions and disclose their fossil fuel-related assets.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
